Package frc.discordslackbot

Class MessageHandler

java.lang.Object
net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
frc.discordslackbot.MessageHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.EventListener
public class MessageHandler
extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
woooooooo handles messages! This class is cool because it is very two-faced. On the one hand, the member methods which are inherited from ListenerAdapter work alongside DiscordBot to handle incoming server side messages. The static methods defined here work with ClientServerPipeline to handle incoming messages clientside.
